abstract: New York Jets quarterback Mark Sanchez and wide receiver Plaxico Burress are struggling to develop harmony on the field; Sanchez has thrown eight deep passes to Burress so far this season, completing three.
snippet: Jets quarterback Mark Sanchez and wide receiver Plaxico Burress are still struggling to develop harmony on the field.
